platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Keep an eye on your shut-eye

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Rather than yanking you from your slumber like an alarm clock, this app analyzes your sleep patterns using your devices microphone, then picks your lightest sleep to rouse you gently.
